snippet.title: Eleusis Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Teaser Trailer from the new upcoming video game Eleusis. 
A first-person adventure 3d game made with the UDK engine. The story takes place in an seemingly abandoned mountain village where an ancient mystery still lies in it.

For more visit: http://www.eleusisgame.com
